<p class="content-text">
There have been three other pitchers who have hit a home run as well as throwing a no-hitter.
They are: 
Wes Ferrel (1931), Earl Wilson (1962), and Jim Tobin (1944). 
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rick_Wise"> (Source) </a>
</p>

<p class="content-text">
